OL,3,CE-bike fire survivors sue
OL,4,Cmanufacturer, amid government safety
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FTwelve survivors of a fatal flat fire
OL,8,Fcaused by an e-bike battery in east
OL,9,FLondon are taking legal action against
OL,10,Fthe bike manufacturer and property
OL,11,Flandlords.
OL,13,FMizanur Rahman, 41, died in hospital
OL,14,Fafter the flat at Maddocks House,
OL,15,FShadwell went up in flames in the
OL,16,Fearly hours of 5 March 2023.
OL,18,FThe fire started after one of the
OL,19,Fother tenants put their e-bike battery
OL,20,Fon charge overnight and it began
OL,21,Fsparking.
