OL,7,FIt is believed the lithium battery,
OL,8,Fwhich had apparently been used, cared
OL,9,Ffor and charged in accordance with
OL,10,Finstructions, was defective.
OL,12,FOne of the survivors, Nazmush
OL,13,FShahadat, told ITV News London about
OL,14,Fthat night: "We didn't know what to
OL,15,Fdo, what was happening, we just
OL,16,Fpanicked ... I was trying to wake
OL,17,Feverybody but suddenly there was smoke
OL,18,Feverywhere ... We were standing here
OL,19,Fwatching everything burn."
