OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FMr Shahadat also spoke of the lasting
OL,8,Fimpact of the loss of his flatmate.
OL,10,F"We felt so guilty, every one of us
OL,11,Fmanaged to get out, but we couldn't
OL,12,Fbring out one more, the last one ...
OL,13,FSometimes I feel like I died that day
OL,14,Fand everything else is just a dream,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,17,FThe group is now suing the e-bike
OL,18,Fmanufacturer Leon Cycle for personal
OL,19,Finjury and loss.
