OL,7,FImran Khan KC, who is representing the
OL,8,Fgroup, said he hopes the case will
OL,9,Fcreate positive change.
OL,11,F"This is the first case, we think, of
OL,12,Fa claim under these provisions for
OL,13,Fthis kind of trauma and we think it
OL,14,Fwill open the floodgates to other
OL,15,Fpeople coming forward.
