OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"The importance of the claim is not
OL,8,Fthe money aspect of it - although all
OL,9,Fof these individuals deserve
OL,10,Fcompensation - but to hold those
OL,11,Fpeople accountable, who have been
OL,12,Fmaking a lot of money out of providing
OL,13,Fvery defective and bad products and
OL,14,Fcausing harm and suffering to
OL,15,Findividuals," he said.
OL,17,FITV News London has approached Leon
OL,18,FCycle for comment but has not yet
OL,19,Freceived a response.
