OL,4,Cmanufacturer, amid government safety
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the group is also seeking
OL,8,Fdamages from the landlords of the
OL,9,Fproperty, Sofina Begum, 50, and Aminur
OL,10,FRahman, 53, - who is no relation to
OL,11,Fthe victim - for the way the flat was
OL,12,Fmaintained, which they described as
OL,13,F"overcrowded, uninhabitable and
OL,14,Finherently dangerous".
OL,16,FAn investigation by Tower Hamlets
OL,17,FCouncil found the two-bedroom flat was
OL,18,Flicensed to accommodate three people,
OL,19,Fbut had been converted to house 20
OL,20,Fpeople, with sets of bunk beds in both
OL,21,Fbedrooms and the living room.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
