OL,4,Cmanufacturer, amid government safety
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FThe tenants also say the flat was in
OL,8,Fpoor condition, with black mould and
OL,9,Fbeg bugs, and had no fire extinguisher
OL,10,For fire doors.
OL,12,FMs Begum and Mr Rahman have since
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to criminal charges
OL,14,Fbrought against them by Tower Hamlets
OL,15,FCouncil relating to their management
OL,16,Fof the flat. They are due to be
OL,17,Fsentenced in December.
OL,19,FITV News London has also contacted Ms
OL,20,FBegum and Mr Rahman for comment.
