OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FAccording to London Fire Brigade, the
OL,8,Ffire in Shadwell is not an isolated
OL,9,Fincident
OL,11,FLFB said it attended 143 e-bike fires
OL,12,Fand 36 e-scooter blazes last year,
OL,13,Fcausing a total of three deaths and
OL,14,Fleaving around 60 people injured.
OL,16,FFires involving lithium batteries `
OL,17,Fwhich are used for e-bikes and e-
OL,18,Fscooters ` can spread rapidly and
OL,19,Fproduce a toxic vapour.
