OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FThe government has now launched a
OL,8,Fcampaign warning consumers over the
OL,9,Ffire risks associated with e-bikes and
OL,10,Fe-scooters bought from rogue online
OL,11,Fsellers.
OL,13,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,14,F(DBT) is calling on the public to:
OL,16,FIt warned that faulty parts have
OL,17,Fresulted in hundreds of incidents
OL,18,Facross the UK where the electric
OL,19,Fmobility devices have caught fire,
OL,20,Fsome of which have resulted in deaths.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
