OL,3,CE-bike fire survivors sue
OL,4,Cmanufacturer, amid government safety
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FProducts sold which do not meet UK
OL,8,Fsafety standards have been found to be
OL,9,Fmore at risk of exploding and catching
OL,10,Ffire, particularly when being charged.
OL,12,FThe DBT said many fires are caused by
OL,13,Fparts being fitted to e-bikes or e-
OL,14,Fscooters which are incompatible, as
OL,15,Fwell as by defective components.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
