OL,3,CE-bike fire survivors sue
OL,4,Cmanufacturer, amid government safety
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FProduct safety minister Justin Madders
OL,8,Fsaid e-bikes can be "a great way to
OL,9,Ftravel" but "we've all seen the tragic
OL,10,Fstories of unsafe e-bikes and e-
OL,11,Fscooters causing dangerous fires and
OL,12,Ftaking lives".
OL,14,FHe added: "We're urging everyone to
OL,15,Fcheck what you're buying, check where
OL,16,Fyou're buying it from and ensure it's
OL,17,Fsafe to use."
